## WebWorkerEngine.(constructor)

Create an instance of WebWorkerEngine, it will create a worker with specified url.

**Signature:**

```typescript

```

| Parameter | Type   | Description                                                                                      |
| --------- | ------ | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ |
